# Eval iteration data — regenerable by re-running evals
# Key findings are captured in RESULTS.md, skill-snapshots/, and review data
# committed selectively (e.g. review loop convergence logs, benchmark.json)
#
# We gitignore the bulk of iteration output and commit only:
#   - eval_metadata.json (eval definitions)
#   - benchmark.json (aggregated results)
#   - review loop data (convergence logs, reviewer JSONs)
#   - RESULTS.md (human-written analysis)

# All iteration variants (iteration-3, iteration-4-improved, iteration-products-0, etc.)
iteration*/**/outputs/
iteration*/**/workspace/
iteration*/**/timing.json
iteration*/**/grading.json
iteration*/**/*-review.json
